Package com.terei.jvector.plugin

Interface Summary
ImagePlugin An interface that must be extended to create a class to save JVector image to other various image formats (eg JPG).
 

Class Summary
ImagePluginManager This class manages all the Image plugins, loading and referencing them for use by other components.
JpgPlugin An ImagePlugin that allows the saving of a JVector Image to a JPG image.
PngPlugin An ImagePlugin that allows the saving of a JVector Image to a PNG image.
SvgPlugin An ImagePlugin that allows the saving of a JVector Image to a SVG image.
